fix: include correct headers for gcc 13 (#7025)

Due to changes in upstream gcc[0], surge no longer builds from source
(a.k.a. FTBFS).

This patch adds the required headers throughout the project, thankfully
it is only one location!

[0]: https://gcc.gnu.org/gcc-13/porting_to.html#header-dep-changes